lead_paragraph: Rafa Nadal was exhausted yet exhilarated following his emotional return to action at this month's Rio Olympics after an injury-absence and is looking forward to gearing back up for the U.S. Open starting on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Aims to Carry Olympic Boost Into US Open
